 I think that the treatment of Beike is very advanced. It includes a series of rehabilitation treatments. 

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:22.710
 When we were looking for stem cell therapy, there were many institutions that did not provide rehabilitation. 

00:03:22.710 --> 00:03:27.310
 They also do not provide functional medicine. 

00:03:27.310 --> 00:03:32.180
 I believe that a large number of assisted rehabilitation treatments provided by Beike 

00:03:32.180 --> 00:03:33.660
 To do what they need to do, are promoting stem cells to their fullest effect, 

00:03:35.300 --> 00:03:40.660
 Including physical therapy, occupational therapy and spa 

00:03:40.660 --> 00:03:47.820
 I can feel it from the first time I receive stem cell treatment. 

00:03:47.830 --> 00:03:49.760
 This series of rehabilitation treatments greatly support the role of stem cells in the body. 

00:03:51.260 --> 00:03:55.540
 Although we didn't see the treatment effect right away, 

00:03:55.550 --> 00:03:59.650
 But Kaden insists on rehabilitation every day to see that stem cells work slowly every day. 

